rows.label: qst202318_0010
rows.name:
It's no good!
There's no way to stop it!

rows.label: qst202318_0020
rows.name: I'm gonna run dry...if it keeps coming at us like this!

rows.label: qst202318_0030
rows.name: It's not showing any signs of stopping...

rows.label: qst202318_0040
rows.name:
Kill it too difficult!
Maybe that why it was sealed in first place...

rows.label: qst202318_0050
rows.name:
Tora's right!
We should have left well alone...

rows.label: qst202318_0060
rows.name:
Nuh-uh!
At least it's finally living up to its name!

rows.label: qst202318_0070
rows.name:
We've run into a half-decent monster for once.
I'm having a great time!

rows.label: qst202318_0080
rows.name:
Well, let's do it!
Nothing for it but to give it everything I've got!
